          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2015-04-06T21:20:39Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Vulnerable Immigrant Voice Act </strong></p> <p>Amends the Immigration and Nationality Act to require that counsel at the government's expense in a removal or related appeal proceeding shall be provided only for an alien who is: (1) an unaccompanied child, or (2) unable to represent himself or herself due to a serious mental disability.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2015-03-26T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
